Can you provide insight on J.K. Rowling's educational and professional backgrounds that may have impacted her writing style and themes in her works? Additionally, can you elaborate on her literary inspirations and the extent to which her works have influenced the young adult fiction genre?
As a reference, here is some Swift code that retrieves information on J.K. Rowling's education and profession:
let url = URL(string: "https://en.wikipedia.org/w/api.php?action=query&format=json&prop=extracts&titles=J.K._Rowling&exintro=1&explaintext=1")!
URLSession.shared.dataTask(with: url) { data, response, error in
    if let data = data {
        if let jsonString = String(data: data, encoding: .utf8) {
            if let json = try? JSONSerialization.jsonObject(with: data, options: []),
               let query = json["query"] as? [String: Any],
               let pages = query["pages"] as? [String: Any],
               let page = pages.first?.value as? [String: Any],
               let extract = page["extract"] as? String {
                // use extract variable to retrieve relevant information
            }
        }
    }
}.resume()
